  <!-- PP -->
  <Section bg="white" id="privacy">
    <SectionTitle color="green" textalign="left"> Privacy Policy </SectionTitle>

    <div class="mt-[2rem]">
      <ul class="mt-[1rem] flex flex-col gap-y-[1rem]">
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">Introduction</h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            D2L.sg is committed to respecting your privacy and ensuring the
            security of your Personal Information. We strive to treat your data
            with the utmost care and have implemented robust protocols to ensure
            its confidentiality. This Privacy policy outlines how we collect,
            use, disclose, and safeguard your information. By using our
            services, you consent to the data practices described in this
            policy.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">
            Collection of Personal Information
          </h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            We collect Personal Information to provide better services to all
            our users. Personal Information refers to any data that can identify
            you as an individual. This includes, but is not limited to, your
            name, contact details, employment information, educational
            background, billing and payment information, and other relevant
            details related to your use of our products, services, websites, or
            job applications. We collect this information when you:
            <br />
            Register or interact with our website
            <br />
            Use our products or services
            <br />
            Communicate with us via email, phone, or other means
            <br />
            Participate in our surveys or promotions
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">Use of Personal Information</h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            By providing your Personal Information to D2L.sg, you consent to the
            following uses:
            <br />
            Collection, Retention, and Disclosure: We may collect, retain, use, and
            disclose your Personal Information for our records and those of our affiliates.

            <br />
            Communication: We may contact you via telephone, email, or other means
            to inform you about products, services, and updates that may interest
            you.

            <br />
            Service Improvement: We use your information to enhance our services,
            verify compliance with our policies, and meet legal obligations.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">Sharing Personal Information</h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            We may share your Personal Information with:
            <br />
            Affiliates and partners for business purposes
            <br />
            Regulatory authorities
            <br />
            Lawyers, accountants, auditors, or other advisors
            <br />
            Third-party service provider who assist in our operations
            <br />
            Agents acting on our behalf
            <br />
            We do not sell or disclose your Personal Information to third parties
            for their marketing purposes without your explicit consent.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            In certain situations, we may use or disclose your Personal
            Information without your consent, such as when required by law, for
            research or statistical purposes, or in emergencies that threaten
            life, health, or security.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">Data Security</h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            D2L.sg employs industry-standard practices to safeguard your
            Personal Information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.
            While we strive to protect your data, we cannot guarantee absolute
            security due to inherent limitations in current technology. We will
            take all reasonable steps to protect your data from misuse, loss,
            unauthorized access, modification, or disclosure.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">Respecting Your Choice</h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            We comply with the Do Not Call (DNC) provisions under the Personal
            Data Protection Act. If you have registered your Singapore telephone
            number with the national DNC Registry, we will refrain from sending
            you marketing messages unless expressly allowed by law or if you
            have given us prior consent.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">
            Access and Correction of Personal Information
          </h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            You have the right to request details about your Personal
            Information held by D2L.sg and to correct any inaccuracies. If you
            wish to review or update your information, please contact us at
            hello@d2l.sg .
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">Record Retention</h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            Your Personal Information will be retained only as long as necessary
            for the purposes outlined in this policy as required by law. Once
            your data is no longer needed, or if you request deregistration, we
            will securely destroy or de-identify your information.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">Amendments</h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            D2L.sg reserves the right to amend this Privacy Policy from time to
            time. Your continued use of our services after the changes have been
            made constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-orange font-bold">Opting Out</h4>
          <p class="mt-[1rem]">
            You may opt out of receiving marketing communications from D2L.sg by
            contacting us at hello@d2l.sg. Please note that you may still
            receive non-marketing communications, such as service updates and
            legal notices.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
